python - <<'PY'
import requests, json
url='https://api.cellxgene.cziscience.com/dp/v1/collections/search'
# try query for dataset_id in collection? maybe 'datasets.id'??
for payload in [
    {'where': {'datasets': {'id': '21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde'}}},
    {'where': {'dataset_id': '21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde'}},
    {'where': {'datasets.id': '21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde'}},
    {'where': {'id': '21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde'}},
]:
    try:
        r=requests.post(url, json=payload, timeout=20)
        print('payload', payload, 'status', r.status_code, r.headers.get('content-type'))
        print(r.text[:200])
    except Exception as e:
        print('error', e)
